OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foccasionally heavy rain in the east at
OL,7,Ffirst. Drier, clearer weather in the
OL,8,Fwest will spread to all through the
OL,9,Fevening. Mostly dry overnight, few
OL,10,Fshowers in northwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FDry and bright in the east in
OL,13,Fthe morning, a few showers in west.
OL,14,FBright or sunny spells and scattered
OL,15,Fshowers everywhere in the afternoon,
OL,16,Fheavy and thundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
