OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,7,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday, heavy and
OL,8,Fthundery at times. Turning windier
OL,9,Fwith widespread cloud and rain
OL,10,Farriving from the west on Thursday.
